(151, 1, '2019-06-21 23:34:45', '2019-06-21 16:34:45', '<div id="pl-151"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-151-0"  class="panel-grid panel-has-style"  data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;li_full&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div class="li_full panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-151-0" ><div id="pgc-151-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-151-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div id="pl-w5d2055dd68ba2"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-w5d2055dd68ba2-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-w5d2055dd68ba2-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-w5d2055dd68ba2-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget">In just one visit, you will discover all the products, ideas, people, technologies and information you need for the future success of your business.\n\nVIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020 is expected to have nearly 100 booths, including more than 50 foreign enterprises from 20 countries and territories.</div></div></div></div><div id="pg-w5d2055dd68ba2-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}" ><div id="pgc-w5d2055dd68ba2-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-w5d2055dd68ba2-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="1" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Enjoy a dynamic program of FREE seminars to challenge and inform, with specialized topic streams and an impressive line-up of expert speakers.</li>\n 	<li>Join in the lively debates and gain valuable insights into today’s key issues.</li>\n 	<li>Connect with your Vietnam and global peers.</li>\n</ul></div></div></div><div id="pgc-w5d2055dd68ba2-1-1"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-w5d2055dd68ba2-1-1-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Current and future product and service offerings – know how to better manage, budget and anticipate requirements</li>\n 	<li>The standards and regulatory framework – essential information to keep you legal</li>\n 	<li>All of which have serious implications for your ability to deliver and manage cost effective and innovative lift and lifting solutions for the built environment.</li>\n</ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Why Visit', 'Coming to the exhibition will be known about current and future product and service services - know how to better manage, budget and predict requirements', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-visit', '', '', '2019-09-08 12:49:00', '2019-09-08 05:49:00', '', 0, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/?p=151', 0, 'post', '', 0);
