(275, 1, '2019-06-23 15:36:15', '2019-06-23 08:36:15', '<div id="pl-84"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-84-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-84-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-84-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;ul_check  why_exhybit&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="ul_check  why_exhybit panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-84-0-0-0" ><div class="textwidget">No other event gathers many important decision makers over a two-day period. More than 2,700 visitors with real purchasing power attended the exhibition, all looking forward to meeting new suppliers, finding new products, networks and forming new business relationships.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-84-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}" ><div id="pgc-84-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="1" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Only dedicated market place for the LIFT, Escalator &amp; Access Industry in the UK</li>\n 	<li>It is your industry event designed to help you generate business for the next 3 years</li>\n 	<li>Opportunity to meet £665m of potential business in just two d