 Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Nepal, Japan, China are officially countries and territories that were officially present at Vietnam Expo at this time, it is expected that this year''s Fair will attract businesses to attend from 20 countries and territories, along with over 15,000 trade visitors to visit and work in the 4th time. Fair day.</span>\r\n<figure></figure>\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Vietnam Expo 2019 is chaired by the Ministry of Industry and Trade, directed by the Vietnam Trade Promotion Agency and organized by VINEXAD, which will be open from 9am to 6pm on 10-13 April 2019 at the Exhibition Center 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi. Details of the Fair at: www.vnexpocom.vn</span>', 'About Elevator 2020', 'With the history of being one of the most prestigious and long-standing trade promotion events in Vietnam, Vietnam Expo has always affirmed that through every year of organization and in 2019 - after a year of prosperity of the Vietnamese economy. Men, import-export turnover and investment all have signs of encouraging growth, we continue to promote the role of an event to promote import-export trade and investment, bringing Vietnamese products to promote. to the world and vice versa.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-03 20:51:02', '2019-07-03 13:51:02', '', 64, 'http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/64-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
