(584, 1, '2019-09-07 21:46:27', '2019-09-07 14:46:27', '<p style="text-align: center;">Welcome to Vietnam trade fair for confectionery, sweets and snacks industry!</p>\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-581 size-full aligncenter" src="http://vietfood.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/keo-1.jpg" alt="" width="703" height="207" />\r\n\r\nVietnam trade fair for confectionery and snacks offers inspiration and innovation, exciting networking possibilities, top-class exhibitors and competent visitors. This perfect combination is unique around the globe. You will also find the world’s largest offer of trademark confectionery and snacks. Discover international confectionery and snacks at the confectionery and snacks trade fair in Vietnam.\r\n\r\nConfectioner and Snacks presents the entire supplier range of the sweets and snacks industry: from diverse ingredients through innovative packing machines and packaging materials to optimized product technologies. Be part of it and present your products and services!\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=h%C3%ACnh+%E1%BA%A3nh+hai+tay+b%E1%BA%AFt+nhau&amp;rlz=1C1CHZL_enVN847VN847&amp;tbm=isch&amp;source=iu&amp;ictx=1&amp;fir=qF1keK5_0yOweM%253A%252Cj_lMfq8M8zGeuM%252C_&amp;vet=1&amp;usg=AI4_-kQSStKasxCM0d-y0KzH19_jnoaugg&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjUqNS0z7PkAhUOIIgKHe1zDJ4Q9QEwAHoECAkQBg#imgrc=qF1keK5_0yOweM:&amp;vet=1">https://www.google.com/search?q=h%C3%ACnh+%E1%BA%A3nh+hai+tay+b%E1%BA%AFt+nhau&amp;rlz=1C1CHZL_enVN847VN847&amp;tbm=isch&amp;source=iu&amp;ictx=1&amp;fir=qF1keK5_0yOweM%253A%252Cj_lMfq8M8zGeuM%252C_&amp;vet=1&amp;usg=AI4_-kQSStKasxCM0d-y0KzH19_jnoaugg&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjUqNS0z7PkAhUOIIgKHe1zDJ4Q9QEwAHoECAkQBg#imgrc=qF1keK5_0yOweM:&amp;vet=1</a>\r\n\r\nHand in hand: In co-operation with Confectioner and Snacks, the international supplier trade fair for the confectionery and snacks industry, Confectioner and Snacks represents the entire industrial value chain. From August 15 to August 18 in 2020, the trade fair duo will once again turn the HoChiMinh city into the hotspot of the confectionery and snacks industry.\r\n\r\nThe Future &amp; Heart of Sweets &amp; Snacks\r\n\r\nThe International supplier trade fair of the sweets and snacks industry in Vietnam\r\n\r\nThe International supplier trade fair fair for confectionery sweets and snacks industry in Vietnam\r\n\r\nThe trade fair for confectionery and snacks!\r\n\r\nA BIGGER SELECTION OF PRODUCTS\r\n\r\nExplore the complete spectrum of products and resources – exhibitors represent every segment of the grain based foods industry across the entire vertical supply chain, including:\r\n\r\nProduct index\r\n<ul class="ul_check">\r\n 	<li>Baking equipment and technology</li>\r\n 	<li>Ingredients, flavorings, spices and fillings</li>\r\n 	<li>Packaging materials and systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Refrigeration equipment</li>\r\n 	<li>Sanitation equipment</li>\r\n 	<li>Transportation and distribution</li>\r\n 	<li>chocolate, chocolate products</li>\r\n 	<li>sugar confectionery</li>\r\n 	<li>biscuits</li>\r\n 	<li>snack foods</li>\r\n 	<li>savoury snacks, ready-to-serve</li>\r\n 	<li>fruit snacks and vegetable snacks</li>\r\n 	<li>breakfast</li>\r\n 	<li>ice cream, deep-frozen confectionery</li>\r\n 	<li>other</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="https://www.ism-cologne.com/exhibitors-and-products/product-index/product-index-10.php">https://www.ism-cologne.com/exhibitors-and-products/product-index/product-index-10.php</a>  vào đây để copy danh muc sp trưng bày\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.prosweets.com/exhibitors-and-products/product-index/product-index-14.php">https://www.prosweets.com/exhibitors-and-products/product-index/product-index-14.php</a>\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-577" src="http://vietfood.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/keo1.png" alt="" width="233" height="195" />\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.fimcobase.com/Contact_Us_FimcoBase.aspx">http://www.fimcobase.com/Contact_Us_FimcoBase.aspx</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.ism-cologne